---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Roots of Tomorrow">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-20 pb-12 sm:pt-28">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-600 text-canopy sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
      Your privacy is important to us at Roots of Tomorrow. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you visit our website.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-8">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-600 text-canopy">1. Information Collection</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
          We collect information that you voluntarily provide when using our services, such as your name, email address, and phone number.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-600 text-canopy">2. Use of Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
          The information we gather is used to provide and improve our services, process transactions, send periodic emails, and tailor your experience on our website. We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-600 text-canopy">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
          We implement a variety of security measures to protect your personal data. However, no data transmission over the internet is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-600 text-canopy">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
          We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist in operating our website, conducting our business, or servicing you, under strict confidentiality agreements.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-600 text-canopy">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
          You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@rootsoftomorrow.org" class="text-leaf hover:underline">contact@rootsoftomorrow.org</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 leading-relaxed text-soil/70">
      By using our website, you consent to our Privacy Policy. We reserve the right to update this policy periodically, and any changes will be posted on this page.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
